direction1= input("Oh No! You are lost on the island without your map and you've reached a fork in the road. You don't know why way is the right way but you have to decide. Where do you want to go? Type 'left' or 'right'")
print('''.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.-.
